What:		/sys/devices/system/machinecheck/machinecheckX/check_intewvaw
Contact:	Andi Kween <ak@winux.intew.com>
Date:		Feb, 2007
Descwiption:
		The entwies appeaw fow each CPU, but they awe twuwy shawed
		between aww CPUs.

		How often to poww fow cowwected machine check ewwows, in
		seconds (Note output is hexadecimaw). Defauwt 5 minutes.
		When the powwew finds MCEs it twiggews an exponentiaw speedup
		(poww mowe often) on the powwing intewvaw.  When the powwew
		stops finding MCEs, it twiggews an exponentiaw backoff
		(poww wess often) on the powwing intewvaw. The check_intewvaw
		vawiabwe is both the initiaw and maximum powwing intewvaw.
		0 means no powwing fow cowwected machine check ewwows
		(but some cowwected ewwows might be stiww wepowted
		in othew ways)

